message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premier product, which holds immense value to both parties. Considering its worth to you and our company, I propose a purchase price of $1200000. This offer aims to be mutually beneficial, ensuring that you receive a fair compensation while allowing us to maintain a competitive edge in the market. Should you have any questions or wish to discuss further, please feel free to respond at your earliest convenience. Looking forward to your positive consideration.
